author: @hannahdy9697
text:
Hello, let me introduce NCT's main vocalist Doyoung to everyone here :)

The talented and amazing singer that he is:
1. His performance on King of Masked Singers https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLptT-Koxq1ra3xWixuVjlgijHQZKJW4VC

2. All his OSTs, solo song, collabs, covers, stations, special projects, vocal compilation and pre-debut performances https://youtube.com/playlist?list=PLO_Bn7ySaxWstBnlgiGKYXPmbk10taX1T

3. Fancams https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLcKTuMwiBpH0DEEAESzfSD2qWYqr6DU26 

For a glimpse of how amazing he is as a person and how passionate and dedicated he is as a singer you can watch these videos:
1. Short compilation of his personality. For newer ones you can look up for his fan accounts on Twitter https://youtu.be/a5gasT-haGc 
 
2. He prepared these KoMS stages while he was busy with tours, comebacks and flying in and out of the country https://youtu.be/bGLYLQDazjo

Doyoung also debuted as an actor with a short drama called Cafe Midnight (심야카페) Season 3 'The Curious Stalker' last year. Check out the trailer here: https://youtu.be/giEF7Rbg6yo 

Later on, he made his first appearance as musical actor in the musical Marie Antoinette and received great praises from seniors of the industry as well as the audiences.

His Instagram: instagram.com/do0_nct

He is the first ever K-pop artist that I fully stan starting 2017 although I've been listening to K-pop music way longer than that. He is not only an amazing artist but also has beautiful heart and always does his absolute best to connect with his fans. I hope this short introduction will interest any of you to check him further. Please give this gem a lot of love and support! ❤️

I decided to create blog a couple of months ago, because I wanted to share that passion with as many people as possible. If you also are passionate about kmusic and dramas, or know people that are, you can visit my blog and follow me on social media: @t. You'll find multiple topics: Monthly top kmusic, drama reviews, group/artist presentations, and even briefings of big news in the Korean entertainment industry. Thank you so much for giving me a bit of your time, and I wish you a lovely day!

author: @andrea5461
text: I don't know if criticism is accepted here and this is nothing against Doyoung personally. He has a very strong but soothing voice, but the breath control here is not great. It's quite breathy. Maybe it's his style but personally it bothered me. A lot of consonants sound too harsh which means you can hear the puffs of air as he pushes through them. Also, when he sings, "what am I now? what am I now?", he changes volumes, going for a much softer sound at the end, but you you can hear the air he's not using kinda flowing into the microphone? Might be intentional but I doubt it. He might be an amazing singer but I do think this cover needed a bit more rehearsing.

Doyoung: he’s crumbling down after he lost his lover but acts fine, suppressing his emotions so no one would know. he’s falling after he lost his lover but acts fine, suppressing his emotions so no one would know. It’s a burden that he chose to keep himself.

author: @culturetechs
text: I don't usually prefer ballads or songs with slower tempos, but Doyoung has successfully lured me in. His delivery is always top-notch -- regardless if it's in the recording booth, at a live concert, or in a cover like this. He doesn't sing for the sake of ~showing emotion~ or making it sound like he's going through his 3rd divorce. He sings with emotions because that's what he does best -- telling stories through his singing. His voice is equally soothing and comforting as it is powerful and compelling. He makes you want to listen to him. He's right. Everytime he sings I just keep falling and falling again.

author: @ddovelylee3947
text:
도영아.... 갈수록 실력이 더 느는 게 보여서 팬으로서 너무 뿌듯하고 고맙고ㅠㅠ 
팬들이 좋아했던 것 같아서 다시 제대로 불러봤다는.. 그 예쁜 마음 어떻게 갚아줄 수 있을까.. 

너가 노래를 사랑하는 모습이 그 어떤 가수보다 강하게 와 닿아서 항상 알면서도 많이 놀라고 감동받고 그래..
북미투어 때도  스스로 계획해서 그 낯선땅에서 버스킹영상 찍어 올린 것부터 상당히 큰 충격줬었는데 갈수록 여기저기서 최대한 활용할 수 있는 많은 것들을 이용해 노래를 들려주고 진심을 전해주려 해서 감동 받고 또 받고.. 익숙해지지 않는 감동이야ㅠㅠ

븨앱을 켜도, 라방을 켜도 항상 노래는 꼭 불러주는.. 콘서트까지도 열어주는 기특한 멤버.. 
언젠가 복면가왕에서 아이돌이라는 것에 자부심이 있다고 했는데 그 자신감, 자부심이 너를 발전시키고, 더 큰 사람으로 성장시키는 것 같아서.. 이런 아이돌의 팬이라 벅차고 뿌듯해!
너는, 엔시티 멤버들은 언제나 성장하고 발전하고 있는 게 보이니까 항상 자신감 잃지 말고 더더 오래오래 팬들한테 노래 불러줄 수 있는 가수가 되어줘! 
오랜만에 올라온 커버영상에 너무 벅차서 너무 주저리주저리..그래도 이것도 다 표현 못하고 줄인거야ㅠㅠ 

김도영 장하다. 자랑스럽다! 엔시티 더 성공하자!

author: @user-zg7cr6pb2l
text:
Doyoung’s voice srsly heals my empty soul... nowadays we might feel empty, tiring, depressed or unhappy and the world rn might be a whole chaos (eg. Covid pandemic, cruel ppl disrespecting/mistreating one other, racism, unfair treatment, betrayal, situation that causes mental health problems (depression or anxiety)) 
But I’m really glad that besides all these negative things...they are still angels that save our life and make our life better...(Words can’t describe how grateful I am that I have Nct in my life.. I’m really thankful for the existence of nct... they made our life better... they make me find more hope and meaning in life...sometimes I think the world is so cruel and that life is pointless/hopeless... but Nct is the one that given me strength... they gave me strength to continue to live a life despite of all the negatives. Everytime I hear their voices and their songs it completely heals my soul... the moment I hear their voices it’s like suddenly all the worries, negative things are all gone... oso it’s makes me think that the world aren’t that bad after all and that there are always meaning in life.... it is like a free therapy for me... they are really an inspiration to me... from the bottom of my heart Im rlly rlly thankful to nct for appearing in my life (thank you so so much and luv u guys forever💚💚💚) 
I strongly believe that Nct deserve more and they deserve the whole world... their talents, personalities, kindness should get more recognition like for real...they are the number one💯🥇 (their vocals, dances, raps, visuals are undefeatable) 
Nct World Domination🌍💚💚💚⭐️⭐️⭐️
I hope all nct, nctzens and even non nctzens are doing well at life whilst the pandemic... 
Let’s stay together forever... we are one family and the greatest fandom  “Nctzen” 💚💚⭐️⭐️ 
(Sorry for my bad English haha lol) 
Anyways have a great one everyone... u guys are all amazing and all did well today ...yoshi yoshi everyone 💚💚💚⭐️⭐️⭐️

(Although no one will read this but still I wanna show my appreciation hehe💚⭐️)

author: @mochideceased42
text:
this cover showcases the different beautiful vocal colours of doyoung. we have the soft colour we usually see and are familiar with in dy's parts in nct songs(0:15). we can see the amazing vocal control in the chorus(0:48), and we see the weak, beautiful, desperate colour(1:49). we also have the strong, aggressive, eager voice in the end(2:10).
this cover again reminds me of how good of a vocalist dy is. definitely deserved all the parts in nct's songs. might be one of the leading vocalists in 4th gen in the future. (just like his idol baek in 3rd gen!!) looking forward to more!

author: @alanasparrow4451
text:
I'm not a harry styles fan but I connected with falling when it was released.
Doyoung is one of my fav, if not my fav vocalist in the industry.
Hearing him sing falling brought me to tears as I could feel the emotion in Doyoung's voice, he understood the songs dynamic and he showed it. Falling is one of those songs that always has a memory or a moment attached to it to make you love it, to make you connect with it, to make you feel it. hearing Doyoung sing made me wonder how he connected and it made me sad to think that he might connect to it in the same way others do, with a sad moment or memory. Songs like this however even though connected to sad feelings bring comfort in knowing others feel the same, so to anyone seeking comfort I hope you found it through Falling and through our angle Doyoung.

P.S. Doyoung may not have connected but may have just been able to portray the emotion in his voice.

예고해줬을 때 저번 븨앱에서 부른 블루밍이나 백현 슨배님 노래 기대하긴 했는데 영상 보는 순간 걍 이거 불러줘서 고맙다고 절하고 싶은 마음 뿐.  올해 시작한지 3개월밖에 되지 않았는데 밤공기, 인형, 커버곡, 븨앱 도콘 .. 이미 수많은 노랠 들려줌ㅠㅠㅠㅠ
노래 사랑하고 진심으로 불러주고 팬들한테 항상 들려주고 싶어해서 너무 고마워 김도영!! 
아이돌로, 가수로, 도영으로 오래오래 노래해줘ㅠㅠ
